down\n ip address 10.0.0.2/32\n!\ninterface eth1\n no shutdown\n description x1 -> dut\n ip address 10.0.0.2/32\n!\ndo write\nCONFIG\nvtysh -f /tmp/config\n!\nexit 0\n"
